{"pin":"BH00739","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00739","anchor":"","title":"Lawh-i-Sahab (Tablet of the Cloud)","first_line":"This is a Book from before the Most Merciful unto those who have turned their faces towards Him Who is the Qiblih of all who dwell in the heavens and on earth [3.5s]... ...My captivity can bring on Me no shame. Nay, by My life, it conferreth on Me glory. That which can make Me ashamed is the conduct of such of My followers as profess to love Me","first_line_orig":"هذا کتاب من لدی الرحمن الی الذین اقبلوا الی قبله من فی السموات و الارضین  ","language":"Ara","word_count":"1060","subjects":"@characteristics and conduct of true believers, @chastisement and requital, @teaching the Cause; call to teach, @rejection, opposition and persecution, @proclamation to kings; rulers; prominent individuals, @the power of words; of speech, @predictions and prophecies, @suffering and imprisonment, @the Word of God; influence and centrality of, @power and sovereignty of God; omnipotence of God","notes":" \u003ca href=\"https://bahai-library.com/bahailib/1504.pdf#page=179\"\u003eMMAH.167\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"https://reference.bahai.org/fa/t/o/GS/gs-179.html\"\u003eGSH.179\u003c/a\u003e,  \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#228\"\u003eLL#228\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"it","lang_name":"Italian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"te","lang_name":"Telugu"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"type":"gleanings",